Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been called to the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What lies here is nothing more than\Nthe hollow shell of Richard Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,His soul, though, will live on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us swear on his soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To live our lives with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Psalms 23...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sad funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such a good detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody from the force has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He had alcohol related problems\Nwhile on the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He got drunk and fell off a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what the police are saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:01:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard would have seen his\Ndaughter on the day after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What. .. What did I do for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just sat in a chair and listened to\Nwhat he had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"You've completely recovered"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I ever do for him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If we find him, there's a possibility\Nwe'll be able to solve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's odd, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't an accident!\NThis isn't a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard was talking to his daughter\Na few hours before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They were going to meet the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You did all that you could do and\NRichard was recovering wonderfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop blaming yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband stopped talking to me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,after I found out\Nhe was having an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He just washes the car\Nand cleans the yard everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He even avoids me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's better than not coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to go crazy\Nif this keeps up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I went over to\Nthe other woman's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think happened, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibility of murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any.\NIt was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That evening, Richard Braun went\Nto the roof of building Number Twelve
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,at the University of Munich alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He drank a single bottle of whiskey,\Ngot drunk, and fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottle. ..did you\Ncheck it thoroughly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. ..we found Richard's fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you show me the bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sure, but...it's in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you think it's odd?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Richard was talking to his daughter\Na few hours before he died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were going to meet the next day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this person came here that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't remember that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that you remember\Nwhen he came,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but can't remember\Nif he was with anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. ..it's because he ordered coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual for someone to come in\Nat that time and not order alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, was he with this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NLots of customers came and went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know that\Nhe bought a bottle of whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written on the order slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Richard really buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know that it says one bottle\Nof Racke on the order slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One bottle of Racke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I notice this when I saw\Nthe bottle label at the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you drinking again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well...just a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did you drink?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whiskey! I only drink whiskey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You made my entire room\Nsmell of Racke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Racke?! Are you kidding me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never drink that domestic stuff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'm going to drink,\NI'll drink genuine scotch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing else!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Richard didn't buy the whiskey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Johan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must have been him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to\Nshove me onto the tracks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about your age. Old men should\Nbe looking after their grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trained as\Na border police officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to\Nshove me onto the tracks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate a former officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Someone asked me to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A large man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A large man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy I met in the subway\Ngave me money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to push you\Nonto the tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought you something, Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's genuine scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to have some, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good enough... Have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard...leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure out his. ..Johan's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I told my husband\Nthat his infidelity is a disease
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he should be the one\Nin counseling with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course, Mrs. Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If my husband keeps this up,\Nmy depression will only get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. ..you don't\Nreally have depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm more worried\Nabout your husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,silently washing his car\Nand cleaning the yard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you? It's strange, no matter\Nhow you look at it! Doctor, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Well, I'm open\Nthe day after tomorrow at five o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Straighten out that oversized cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, that's the last of\Nyour appointments for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's good enough\Nfor today, Mereth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be off ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Mereth, you forgot to\Nlock the back door again yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh no. I almost forgot\Nto do it today as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, I did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Gillen... It's Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the newspaper.\NYeah, your newspaper ad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's talk about\Nour memories of cheating."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"From Rudi."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think that Dr. Tenma\Nwill contact us with this message?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... Tenma definitely will\Nif he sees it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's something only the two of us\Nknow about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor, don't do anything rash\Nuntil he comes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...but there's just one thing\NI want to look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The prostitute who pretended to be\NMargot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fahren, the boy who killed himself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was with another boy\Nwhen he met her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A handsome blond boy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I've got to be careful\Nif I want to uncover everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for Richard's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mereth, you've forgotten\Nto close the window today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot Langer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.. .her trade name right now\Nis Blue Sophie or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... That fat old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps, is that what\Nyou're interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shy at your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a turn at the corner,\Ntwo blocks down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The second floor of the old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's not there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her lately.\NShe's probably gone somewhere nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. Why is that fat old hag\Nso popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A really rich guy\Nwas seeing her until recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what do you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lot more fun than that hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where she went?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. She probably went off\Nwith that new guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,New guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He became infatuated\Nwith that hag despite his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Big guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed like he was\Nbig elsewhere as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right if I leave for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, oh yeah. ..\NYou're only working until five today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. The only appointment\NI have left is that cheating husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a date, isn't it, Mereth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure to lock the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to show this picture\Nto the prostitute called Blue Sophie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,who was pretending to be\NMargot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If Johan was with Fahren,\Nand I can get her testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one step closer to\Ngetting to the bottom of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife made the appointment.\NI'm Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, come right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll visit that woman once more tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Mr. Hesse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time\NI've been in counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be nervous about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just relax and talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our conversation will be confidential,\Nso don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even to my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you lately?\NDo you have any concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife...found out about my affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a place at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just clean the yard and wash my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make you feel a little\Nbetter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I never talk to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to talk to her,\Nbut don't have the chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the other woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you broken up with the woman\Nyou were cheating with?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No. ..I saw a dream where I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see dreams like that often?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Often? No. ..I haven't seen any lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you had an affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was after I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A handsome blond boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many people I killed,\Neven when the country fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it all felt like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But. ..that all changed when I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seemed real.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was no longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Would you. ..like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you wait for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My secretary already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems she's got a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Her tea is very good. It's unfortunate\Nthat I can't pour you any of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot happens in\Nthis line of work doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You find out people's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good happens when you\Nfind out a dream you shouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the fact that I'm a hit man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, if you want to fix things\Nwith your wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...talk it over once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hope you forgot to lock\Nthe door today, Mereth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been keeping watch over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in danger. Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
